name: Arthur Abon
text: I wonder what our family and friends who voted Duterte think. I really want to know.    You aren't a drug addict, not part of the media, not a Yellowtard, nor some other demographic that hates Duterte. In our private chats, you were the one who was most chill. I cannot see how this post of yours is maliciously colored in a way to undeservedly disparage the administration.
